Package org.osgi.cdi.api.extension.annotation

Annotation Types Summary
BundleDataFile This annotation qualifies an injection point that represents a bundle data file.
BundleHeader This annotation qualifies an injection point that represents a specific bundle header.
BundleHeaders This annotation qualifies an injection point that represents all headers of a bundle.
BundleName This annotation qualifies an injection point that represents a bundle or a bundle relative object.
BundleVersion This annotation qualifies an injection point that represents a bundle or a bundle relative object.
Filter This annotation qualifies an injection point that represents a LDAP filtered service.
OSGiBundle This annotation qualifies an injection point that represents a bundle or a bundle relative object.
OSGiService This annotation qualifies an injection point that represents a service from the OSGi service registry.
Property This annotation wraps an OSGi service property used for automatic OSGi service publishing.
Publish This annotation notices that this type is an OSGi service implementation and should be automatically published in the OSGi service registry.
Required This annotation qualifies an injection point that represents a required service.
Sent This annotation qualifies an injection point that represents an InterBundleEvent from outside the current Bundle.
Specification This annotation qualifies an injection point that represents events whose match one of the specifications.
